    id: "about",
    title: "About",
    content: "I have been working as a Full Stack Developer at OnePlay LLC, a company dedicated to creating streaming service platforms for various devices and businesses, since May 2023. My role involves building and maintaining web applications using Angular, Laravel, PHP, JavaScript, and TypeScript. I collaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions.",
    active: true,
    image: "/public/images/me.jpg",
  },
  {
    id: "projects",
    title: "Projects",
    content: "At OnePlay LLC, I have contributed to various projects, including developing a scalable e-commerce platform, creating dynamic user interfaces, and implementing RESTful APIs for streaming services. My work ensures seamless user experiences and efficient back-end functionality for diverse streaming platforms.",
    active: false,
    image: "/public/images/me.jpg",
  },
  {
    id: "technologies",
    title: "Technologies",
    content: "My tech stack includes Angular for front-end development, Laravel and PHP for back-end services, and JavaScript and TypeScript for enhancing application functionality. I also utilize various tools and frameworks to streamline development processes, ensuring optimal performance for streaming service platforms.",
    active: false,
    image: "/public/images/me.jpg",
  },
  {
    id: "achievements",
    title: "Achievements",
    content: "Throughout my time at OnePlay LLC, I have achieved significant milestones, such as reducing page load times by 30%, increasing application performance, and leading a team of developers to successfully deliver complex streaming service projects on time.",
